import React from 'react';
import { Container, Typography, Box, Card, CardContent, Button, Grid, TextField } from '@mui/material';
import { useNavigate } from 'react-router-dom';

const Checkout = () => {
  const navigate = useNavigate();

  const handleSubmit = (e) => {
    e.preventDefault();
    // Simulate form submission and payment processing
    const formData = new FormData(e.currentTarget);
    const shippingInfo = {
      name: formData.get('name'),
      email: formData.get('email'),
      phone: formData.get('phone'),
      address: formData.get('address'),
      city: formData.get('city'),
      country: formData.get('country'),
    };

    // In a real application, you would send this data to your backend
    console.log('Shipping Info:', shippingInfo);

    // Redirect to success page after 2 seconds (simulating payment processing)
    setTimeout(() => {
      navigate('/success');
    }, 2000);
  };

  return (
    <Container maxWidth="lg" sx={{ my: 4 }}>
      <Typography variant="h1" component="h1" align="center" gutterBottom>
        Checkout
      </Typography>

      <Card sx={{ mt: 4, p: 4 }}>
        <form onSubmit={handleSubmit}>
          <Grid container spacing={3}>
            <Grid item xs={12} md={6}>
              <Typography variant="h4" gutterBottom>
                Shipping Information
              </Typography>
              <TextField
                fullWidth
                label="Full Name"
                name="name"
                variant="outlined"
                margin="normal"
                required
              />
              <TextField
                fullWidth
                label="Email"
                name="email"
                type="email"
                variant="outlined"
                margin="normal"
                required
              />
              <TextField
                fullWidth
                label="Phone Number"
                name="phone"
                variant="outlined"
                margin="normal"
                required
              />
              <TextField
                fullWidth
                label="Address"
                name="address"
                variant="outlined"
                margin="normal"
                required
              />
              <TextField
                fullWidth
                label="City"
                name="city"
                variant="outlined"
                margin="normal"
                required
              />
              <TextField
                fullWidth
                label="Country"
                name="country"
                variant="outlined"
                margin="normal"
                required
              />
            </Grid>

            <Grid item xs={12} md={6}>
              <Typography variant="h4" gutterBottom>
                Order Summary
              </Typography>
              <CardContent>
                <Typography variant="h5" gutterBottom>
                  Premium Aqua Float
                </Typography>
                <Typography variant="h6" color="primary" gutterBottom>
                  $199.99
                </Typography>
                <Typography variant="body1" paragraph>
                  1 item
                </Typography>
                <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', justifyContent: 'space-between', mt: 2 }}>
                  <Typography variant="h6">
                    Total:
                  </Typography>
                  <Typography variant="h6" color="primary">
                    $199.99
                  </Typography>
                </Box>
              </CardContent>

              <Button
                type="submit"
                variant="contained"
                color="primary"
                size="large"
                fullWidth
                sx={{ mt: 4 }}
              >
                Complete Purchase
              </Button>
            </Grid>
          </Grid>
        </form>
      </Card>
    </Container>
  );
};

export default Checkout;
